                        <interp inst="t18481127-62-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 24.—<hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to Mercy by the Prosecutor and Jury.—
